data.description: Let’s visit this gorgeous country setting of 59096 S. 26th.  Nestled on 2.01 acres of flat grassed land to entertain or set up a tree stand.  This family 4 bedroom home has been updated with custom tile counters, new windows and flooring.  Enjoy your breakfast as you watch the sun rise thru the 4 glass patio doors.  The laundry facilities are located off the kitchen, leaving the full basement available to utilize as you wish. The master suite has a separate vanity/dressing room feature that is unique to any bathroom. Be sure to check out the full list of updates in the supplements.  Visit this well maintained and newly updated home today and Schedule your private appointment with an agent.
